snippet.title: Demolition Robots K.K. | Trailer | Throw the Warped Code Out
snippet.description: Take a peek at indie developer Throw the Warped Code Out’s destruction-based game with Twitch interactivity powered by Genvid Technologies. Destroy cities and build interactions with players and viewers in Demolition Robots K. K.
